@startuml
title FIG-22-01. Choosing the Right Transformation and Migration View
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor #333333
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #F5F7FA
  BorderColor #333333
  FontColor #111111
  RoundCorner 10
}
left to right direction
rectangle "Start with the\ntransformation question" as Start #DCEAF7
rectangle "Current-state baseline" as Current
rectangle "Target architecture" as Target
rectangle "Gap analysis" as Gap
rectangle "Transition architecture" as Transition
rectangle "Dependency map" as Dependency
rectangle "Roadmap or\nmigration-wave view" as Roadmap
rectangle "Cutover or parallel-\noperation view" as Cutover
rectangle "Decommission view" as Retire
rectangle "Benefit map\nor risk view" as Benefit
rectangle "Clarify scope, state,\naudience and decision" as Clarify #FFF2CC
Start --> Current : What evidence describes\nthe current state?
Start --> Target : What state is\nintended?
Start --> Gap : What differs\nbetween states?
Start --> Transition : Can an intermediate state\noperate coherently?
Start --> Dependency : What constrains\nthe order?
Start --> Roadmap : How could change be\ngrouped and sequenced?
Start --> Cutover : How will service or\ndata responsibility move?
Start --> Retire : What evidence permits\nretirement?
Start --> Benefit : Which outcome or\nuncertainty matters?
Start --> Clarify : Still unclear?
@enduml
